%% Example DMTA campaign timeline — worked example from Pillar 3 doc.
%% Objective: "Find an Au(III) candidate active against A2780cis with predicted COL3A1
%% engagement and a synthesis route under 6 steps."

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Chemist
    participant Supervisor as Supervisor agent
    participant Design as Design agent
    participant Synthesis as Synthesis agent
    participant Assay as Assay agent
    participant Analysis as Analysis agent
    participant Tools as inference-api / chemoinformatic-core / retrosynth / ELN / LIMS

    Chemist->>Supervisor: objective + budget + timeframe
    Supervisor->>Design: plan candidate-design phase
    Design->>Tools: generate 20 Au(III) candidates (diffusion + fragment)
    Design->>Tools: rank with target-conditioned MKANO+ (COL3A1)
    Design-->>Supervisor: ranked list of 20
    Supervisor->>Synthesis: retrosynth top 5
    Synthesis->>Tools: AiZynthFinder + IBM RXN
    Synthesis-->>Supervisor: 5 routes with step counts
    Supervisor->>Chemist: Gantt + top-2 candidates for approval
    Chemist-->>Supervisor: approve cand A + cand B

    Synthesis->>Tools: register ELN tasks
    Note over Synthesis,Chemist: chemist executes synthesis manually,<br/>marks ELN entries complete

    Supervisor->>Assay: schedule MTT (A2780, A2780cis), 72h, n=4
    Assay->>Tools: LIMS reservations + power calc
    Note over Assay,Chemist: wet-lab assays performed,<br/>raw data uploaded

    Tools-->>Assay: assay results
    Assay-->>Supervisor: cand A is active in A2780cis (IC50 ~2 µM)

    Supervisor->>Analysis: launch MoA inference on cand A
    Analysis->>Tools: RNA-seq + proteomic correlation + KEGG
    Analysis-->>Supervisor: candidate target list:<br/>COL3A1 (high), BUB1B (mod), PLK1 (low)

    Supervisor->>Chemist: result summary + draft figure
    Chemist->>Supervisor: approve manuscript-draft step
    Supervisor->>Analysis: produce draft results section
    Analysis-->>Chemist: draft manuscript + figure exports
